{"id":682976799,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1 year, 2 months","timestamp":1650307761,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"118 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/682976799/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"47.6 MB","code":"/**\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {number}\n */\nvar romanToInt = function(s) {\n    let map = new Map(), sum = 0, i = 0\n    \n    map.set('M', 1000)\n    map.set('D', 500)\n    map.set('C', 100)\n    map.set('L', 50)\n    map.set('X', 10)\n    map.set('V', 5)\n    map.set('I', 1)\n    \n    while (i < s.length) {\n        let currentSymbol = s.substring(i, i+1)\n        let currentValue = map.get(currentSymbol)\n        let nextValue = 0\n        \n        if (i + 1 < s.length) {\n            let nextSymbol = s.substring(i+1, i+2)\n            nextValue = map.get(nextSymbol)\n        } \n        \n        if (currentValue < nextValue) {\n            sum += (nextValue - currentValue)\n            i+=2\n        }\n        else {\n            sum += currentValue\n            i+=1\n        }\n        \n        \n    }\n    \n    return sum\n    \n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false}
